excerpt.rendered:
DESCRIPTION
Kaytee Songbird Blend Wild Bird Food is one of the highest energy wild bird foods available. This food is specially formulated to attract more colorful songbirds year-round.

Key Benefits:

This unique blend of premium seeds and grains includes peanuts to add even more energy to a mix already rich with black oil sunflower seeds.
KAYTEE Songbird Blend will make your backyard a favorite place for beautiful songbirds.
Specially formulated to attract more colorful songbirds year-round.
